== Ratings ==
In Brazil, the telenovela had average ratings of 21 points and 46% share, reaching over 26 million viewers per day.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://televisao.uol.com.br/noticias/redacao/2014/04/04/com-22-pontos-no-ibope-final-de-joia-rara-se-equipara-a-flor-do-caribe.htm|title=Com 22 pontos no Ibope, final de "Joia Rara" se equipara a "Flor do Caribe"|author=|publisher=[[Universo Online|Uol]]|accessdate=}}</ref> The telenovela's official hashtag, #joiarara, was mentioned 80,000 times, which corresponds to 58% of the total volume of simultaneous online comments. Aired in [[Portugal]], in the [[:pt:Globo (Portugal)|Globo]] basic channel, the plot is daily ranked among the 5 most watched paid TV shows in the country.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.publico.pt/culturaipsilon/noticia/brasileira-joia-rara-bate-a-telenovela-portuguesa-belmonte-nos-emmy-1677469|title=Brasileira Joia rara bate a telenovela portuguesa Belmonte nos Emmy|author=|publisher=Público (Portugal)|accessdate=|language=Portuguese}}</ref>

